Reverse a String
Problem:
Write a method that takes a string and returns its reverse.

Input: A string.
Output: The reversed string.


CODE:



public class demo {
    
    //CREATE METHOD
    
    public static String checkVowel(String str1){
        
        StringBuffer sb = new StringBuffer(str1);
        
       String updated = sb.reverse().toString();
       
       return updated;
      
        
    }
    
    
    public static void main (String [] args){
        
        
        String str = "my name is mission sk";
        
        
        String results = checkVowel(str);
        
        System.out.println(results);
    }
}
